<br>
<br>
<br>
This is taken from the EQ message boards themselves, posted Mr. Arudune(BM) himself.<br>
<br>
If you knowingly kill masses of monsters with a rain spell(which rain spells do of course) you are an exploiter. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uirontreeravenstrike.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Irontree Ravenstrike</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/12/01 7:08:26 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~carriedingus/irontree.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tremor?</span><hr size=1> *scratches head*<br>
